  "body": "We should consider updating the `kubectl wait` command to wait on all resources for a given kind. For example:\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n$ kubectl wait --for=delete pods --all\r\n```\r\n\r\nwould wait for every pod in the current namespace to be deleted.\r\n\r\n/sig cli\r\n\r\ncc @soltysh @deads2k ",
